tweet: I’m excited to see @POTUS reestablish @US_SpaceCom! I join the rest of the CO delegation in urging the @usairforce to make Colorado its permanent home, as it was from 1985 to 2002, to ensure continued U.S. technological superiority, global leadership, and capabilities in space.
